---
title: Pan-Seared Pork Chops and Broccoli Rice with Cheddar Cheese Sauce
description: This '80s-inspired dish has all the comforting flavours of the past, with a fresh '22 twist! Rice and broccoli boil together, while pork chops caramelize in the oven. A melty, creamy cheddar cheese sauce speckled with chives adds modern flair to this classic favourite.
